 vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"note\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/af9bd30e8dd89c5bdc42d67ff5595cb5/e3f56/note.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/af9bd30e8dd89c5bdc42d67ff5595cb5/e3f56/note.png 22w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 22px) 100vw, 22px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    注意事项</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>绘制图例的前提条件是当前布局窗口中存在绘制好了的地图，该地图处于选中状态并且没有被锁定。 </li>\n<li>绘制图例的过程与几何对象的绘制完全一致。</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"title":"绘制图例","next":null,"prev":null},"fields":{"path":"content\\tutorial\\Layout\\DrawingMapElements\\Legend.zh.md","slug":"/zh/tutorial/Layout/DrawingMapElements/Legend/","langKey":"zh"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/zh/tutorial/Layout/DrawingMapElements/Legend/"}}}